'''Cloud Lake''', located in the [[City/Legends|city]] [[Ussa]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bellassa/Legends|Bellassa]], was the one of the seven lakes within the city boundaries, and gave its name to the surrounding city district. Cloud Lake District was adjacent to [[Bluestone District]].

On an outer band of the [[Cloud Lake District]], near a warehouse cluster, was a quiet street that held small businesses and shops, including the business office of [[Ferus Olin]] and [[Roan Lands]], next to [[Dorma's Cafe]], across the street from [[Mariana's Exquisite Designs and Alterations]]. Other businesses on this street included an accounting office, a shop specializing in ceramic [[Teapot/Legends|teapots]] and plates, and an [[Museum/Legends|art gallery]].

After the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] takeover of Bellassa, the local economy of Cloud Lake began to decline, with businesses failing or having to secretly cater to the Imperial garrison.

